IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.manifestweightanalysisreport') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.manifestweightanalysisreport
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.manifestweightanalysisreport (
manifestid int,
billingcustomerid int,
billingcustomer nvarchar(4000),
deliverycustomerid int,
deliverycustomer nvarchar(4000),
parcelno nvarchar(4000),
consignmentcref nvarchar(4000),
weight float,
chargeweight numeric(36,6),
volweight float,
calculatedvolweight numeric(36,6),
calculatedcubes numeric(36,6),
customerbarcode nvarchar(4000),
parceltype nvarchar(4000),
ordercustomereference nvarchar(4000),
ordercorderno nvarchar(4000),
zonelocationdescription nvarchar(4000),

	)

	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/RPT/manifestweightanalysisreport.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.manifestweightanalysisreport 
GO
